Greetings!
Welcome to StarSailor!


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Once this game is started, you can interact with it in a variety of ways.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Whenever prompted to make a choice, type the characters within the [brackets]

then press enter:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
For example, you want to chose the shiny dagger:

   "There are two knives for sale, a shiny dagger and a matte black butterfly knife"
   "[1] Shiny dagger"
   "[2] Matte black butterfly knife"
   "[3] neither"

   >1    **enter**

"you purchased the shiny dagger"
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
After each screen, your stats will appear
you have resources named
[food]
[money]
[sanity]
do not run out of any of them.

If you run out of food, you will die..
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

when entering any text, be exact as you can be, try to avoid typos
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Good luck!!
